        "subject": "LU-5170 lfs: Standardize llapi messages used by lfs_setstripe",
        "message": "LU-5170 lfs: Standardize llapi messages used by lfs_setstripe\n\nStandardize the error messages that can be produced when\nlfs_setstripe() calls llapi functions.  User-provided values are\ndelimited with single quotes.  Messages that duplicate information\nprinted elsewhere are removed.  Message text is more terse.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Steve Guminski <stephenx.guminski@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I264c26db1246507955f1861d6b79d549bf8c1cfd\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
